msgstr ""
"Queremos mapear nuestro host interno (``example_host`` - ``192.168.5.122``) "
"con IP pública ``89.95.145.226``."

#: ../../firewall.rst:299
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`NAT 1:1` panel, we choose for the IP ``89.95.145.226`` "
